devdoc.details: Implements voting process along with vote delegation, proposal addition, vote retraction, and voting deadline.

VotingResults(bytes32,uint256).details: Announce the winner of the voting process by emitting an event.

addProposal(bytes32).details: Add a new proposal. Only the chairperson can call this.

constructor.details: Create a new ballot to choose one of 'proposalNames' with a voting deadline.

delegate(address).details: Delegate your vote to the voter 'to'.

giveRightToVote(address).details: Give 'voter' the right to vote on this ballot. May only be called by 'chairperson'.

retractVote().details: Retract your vote, allowing you to vote again.

params.proposal: index of proposal in the proposals array

winnerName().details: Calls winningProposal() function to get the index of the winner and returns the name of the winner.

returns.winnerName_: the name of the winning proposal

winningProposal().details: Computes the winning proposal taking all previous votes into account.

returns.winningProposal_: index of winning proposal in the proposals array
